<h3>Information</h3>
<div class="paddedcontent">You would wish to know what browsers are being used by your users for the same reason that you would want to know what operating system they are using.  By knowing which browsers are being used to view the site, you can adapt your design strategy to be as inclusive as possible.</div>
<div class="paddedcontent">Almost all websites to a greater or lesser extent find that Microsoft Internet Explorer is the most popular browser chosen by their users.</div>
<div class="paddedcontent">Some of the browsers have been grouped.  To see itemised figures for individual versions of each browser, click the plus sign next to the name of the entry.</div>